DELETION PROCESS
We will delete your personal information within 14 days of receiving your deletion request.
In some cases, we may need longer to delete your personal information, for example, if we need to retain your personal information to comply with legal or regulatory requirements, or to resolve disputes or protect our rights.
We will make every effort to delete your personal information as soon as possible after receiving your request.
DATA TO BE DELETED
We will delete all personal information that we hold about you, including:
Your account information
Your customer support history
Your marketing preferences
EXCEPTIONS
We may not be able to completely delete your personal information in the following cases:
We need to retain your personal information to comply with legal or regulatory requirements.
We need to retain your personal information to fulfill a contract we have with you.
We need to retain your personal information to resolve disputes or protect our rights.
